Description:
Docklands most Desirable Two Bedroom Apartment
A simply stunning Yarras Edge offering with an incredible 148 sqm (approx.) of total space, this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car space apartment defines luxurious and elegant Docklands living. The 02 floorplan in the Tower 5 complex is arguably the most coveted in Yarras Edge, with this layout allowing for wonderful space inside and out including a huge north-facing balcony.
Apartment boasts 125 sqm (approx.) of internal space and 23 sqm (approx.) of outdoor space which is so rare for a 2 bedroom apartment
This property offers you total privacy along with amazing winter sun and shade in summer thanks to the northerly aspect
Enormous undercover balcony has views of the marina below, the mountain ranges to the west, and the city skyline to the east
Expansive central living has enough room for sizeable lounge and dining areas
Practical stone kitchen offers s/steel Miele oven/cooktop, dual Fisher & Paykel dish drawers, and integrated fridge and freezer
Master bedroom provides direct balcony access plus an extra-large WIR/dressing area and double vanity spa ensuite
Other bedroom with BIR and views
Quality second bathroom with walk-in shower and European laundry
Ducted heating and cooling
Secure video intercom entry
2 secure basement car spaces
Storage cage
AMENITIES
Residents of the Tower 5 building will have access to RekDek facilities which include a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
LOCATION
This Lorimer Street location delivers a waterside lifestyle to savour. Enjoy ground floor eateries including the Mad Duck Café and Corniche restaurant, where you can relax and dine while taking in the quiet marina vistas. Youre also not far from IGA supermarket, South Wharf DFO shopping, South Wharf promenade restaurants and bars, Port Melbourne, Southbank, and South Melbourne attractions including Clarendon Street shops, Crown Casino, and South Melbourne Market, free city trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Mia Chen on 0428 096 132 or Mark Sutherland on 0418 691 585 to discuss this property further

Description:
Enjoy the Expanses of this Luxury Docklands Retreat
Stunningly high on the 22nd floor and exhibiting memorable CBD views, expansive internal living, and luxuriously appointed style that will amaze all buyers, this exceptional 3 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom apartment is sheer Docklands bliss that needs to be seen to be believed.
An astonishing amount of natural light, bright floor-to-ceiling windows, stone benchtops, and premium fittings are just the tip of the iceberg for this dazzling property located in the popular Yarras Edge. Its hard to go past the awe-inspiring vistas found throughout the apartment (to the north, west, and south), with the undercover balcony the ultimate spot to enjoy views of the city as well as the Yarra River and Docklands.
A generous living and dining zone includes the state of the art kitchen with a handy island bench and stainless steel Miele appliances. The master bedroom promises terrific privacy and includes a walk-in robe and gorgeous double vanity ensuite with freestanding bath (plus windows with views), while the other bedrooms with BIRs sit opposite a central bathroom that is truly elegant. There is also a large study which could be used as an office for those who work from home.
Other property additions are a separate laundry room, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, two car spaces, and access to an on-site gym as well as RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
On top of all these amazing extras, you get to enjoy the fantastic Yarras Edge precinct which is one of the most sought-after areas in the Docklands. Youre close to the South Wharf Promenade which has bars and eateries such as Plus 5 Bar, Munich Brauhaus, Citizen Café and Bar, and Common Man, while youre also near the Melbourne Exhibition Centre, DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Marvel Stadium, Polly Woodside, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Mia Chen on 0428 096 132 or Jenna Iliopoulos on 0488 488 379 to discuss this property further

Description:
Setting a luxurious and spacious Docklands standard
The ultimate Victoria Harbour package which is an enviable blend of generous living space and dazzling modern interiors, this striking 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom corner apartment in the exclusive Convesso complex is an unmissable opportunity to experience your Docklands dream.
Sitting next to its sister building Concavo, the Convesso complex is one of the Docklands most luxurious and sophisticated complexes with a design by acclaimed
architect Bates Smart
Downsizers and city professionals will be captivated by the fantastic quality throughout this property
Apartment has been freshly painted and enjoys new carpet
Love the generous central living zone which has dedicated carpeted lounge and tiled dining spaces
Central living also features floor-to-ceiling windows which lets in great natural light and gives you charming leafy views
Deluxe kitchen has designer elements including a mosaic tiled splashback plus European appliances
Large corner balcony is undercover and has views out to Bourke Street
Relaxed master bedroom has access to a walk-in robe and ensuite
2nd bedroom with mirrored BIR sits next to the central bathroom with laundry facilities
Ducted heating and cooling
Smart pad video intercom with additional energy monitoring features
Secure car space
Watch our Facebook Live Tour - https://bit.ly/3g9FObs

You will also have access to Convesso facilities which include a 24 hour concierge, communal lounge, business centre and board room, indoor cinema, sky garden with BBQ facilities, 25m indoor heated pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, and treatment room. The Convesso building also has a 5 star energy rating.
LOCATION

Spacious, stylish & convenient
Boasting spectacular sweeping views from the CBD, to the north of Melbourne, and Victoria Harbour, this spacious corner two-bedroom apartment delivers easy-care living with a leisurely lifestyle to match.
The sun-splashed open living/ dining area features an adjoining balcony and is framed by floor-to-ceiling windows which offer unobstructed city views. Effortlessly combining minimalism with functionality, the kitchen is fitted with stone benchtops, high quality stainless steel appliances including a gas stove and integrated dishwasher, glass splashback and ample cabinetry storage.

Additional features include a European laundry, secure car space, split-system heating/cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry.
Residents are merely minutes away from a selection of world leading universities, shopping, cultural and dining destinations, a vast array of public transport options, tranquil gardens and more!

Description:
Docklands Living For The Win
**Contact Claire Spring 0430 144 700**
Open plan living space
Stylish kitchen with gas cook top
Timber floors throughout living space
Light and bright bedroom with access to balcony
Video intercom security
Split-system air conditioning
Exceptional owner occupier/investment potential
Low owners corporation fees $738pq approx. & $170pq approx. of council rates
48sqm approx. of lifestyle living
Rental return of $375 per week ($19,500 pa approx.)
The building is equipped with Swimming pool, Gym, Yoga studio, residents lounge & BBQ deck.
The Victoria Harbour precinct is what the rest of the Docklands want to be. The area is alive with community, culture, business and convenience. Inside of the stylish building located at 889 Collins Street is this well designed, established 1-bedroom apartment with a bright northerly aspect.
The apartment possesses high-end luxury, with a grand lobby entrance with concierge. This theme is continued inside the apartment with an inviting open-plan living dining room with split system air-conditioning and access to the covered balcony. The fully appointed kitchen boasts Miele appliances and ample storage. The carpeted bedroom is fitted with built in robes and the separate luxury bathroom boasting a stone vanity. The apartment is also equipped with a laundry.
Designed by the acclaimed Sydney based architects, Koichi Takada and developed by Lendlease, the design of the building tames the wind creating a harmonious blend of the elements. The apartment interior connects the indoor space to the outdoor environment, whilst maintaining a sense of privacy. The building offers residents access to lap pool and spa, a fully equipped gym and dance room, a dining lounge, a garden area with exercise equipment and a BBQ area.
The tram-stop out the front of the apartment is inside the free tram zone, which encourages access to the City of Melbourne free of charge. The closest train station is Southern Cross, which connects the regional v-line route and interstate passengers to Victoria and the CBD. Southern Cross station is also the city depot for Skybus, the 22-minute airport express which departs every 8 minutes (approx).
The apartment is zoned for South Melbourne Primary School, University High School, and near to the Melbourne University. The building has been cleared of any cladding issues (see attached documentation that explain the materials used in the external cladding of the building).

48m²

Description:
THE QUAY TO UNLOCK THE PERFECT LIFESTYLE
Perfectly placed in one of the Docklands most exclusive complexes, The Quays, this beautifully-appointed and relaxed one bedroom residence embodies modern apartment living that is sure to captivate CBD professionals, first home buyers, and smart investors.
A formal entrance hall takes you directly into the central living and meals zone which boasts floor-to-ceiling windows which opens out to the balcony overlooking stunning Docklands views, an idyllic spot to breathe in the fresh air and enjoy alfresco dining.
The designer kitchen is fitted with quality appliances and the stylish bathroom with vibrant mosaic wall tiles includes a European laundry. With heating, cooling, and a car space this apartment has everything you need for low maintenance apartment living.
The sensational Quays complex offers a Health Club with a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, while there is a Resident's Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. Further enjoy a rooftop garden with tennis court, BBQ and dining facilities.
The NewQuay precinct is a lively hub and home to some of the Docklands best attractions. Trams will take you over all over Melbourne including the MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn, and Box Hill, while surrounding restaurants cover cuisines of all types. You're also moments to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, and the iconic Festival Hall.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

(SOLD) Fabulous Brand New Apartment in Docklands along Yarra River. Free Local Stamp Duty.
This stylish apartment offers a generous open plan living and dining area, a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances and stone bench top, lavish bathrooms, sizable balcony off the living area along with secured entrance, air conditioning and heating.
Featuring first-class onsite building amenities, residents will enjoy secure intercom entry and secure lift access, concierge, indoor lap pool, gym, private residents lounge..
Just a stone's throw away from Woolworths and take the free city-zone tram from your doorstep.
Near Harbour Town Shopping Centre, local cafes and restaurants, Etihad Stadium, CBD attractions, New Quay Promenade, Southern Cross Station, enjoy the convenience of Melbourne city living.

Description:
A stylish slice of the Victoria Harbour precinct
Boasting a brilliant Docklands location that allows you to enjoy all the delights of the Victoria Harbour precinct as well as Melbournes CBD which is so close by, this stylish 2 bedroom apartment in the Watergate North complex is a modern prize that all buyers will desire.
Embrace this brilliant location opposite Docklands Park
Sleek upgraded flooring through living zone and bedrooms
Sizeable central lounge and meals is the perfect everyday living space
Balcony accessed via the living area has a north-east aspect and offers views of CBD
Designer kitchen includes stainless steel benchtops and Smeg appliances
Main bedroom features a study nook, balcony access, and entry to the well-appointed semi-ensuite
Both bedrooms with built-in robes
Laundry facilities
Ducted heating and cooling
Secure intercom
Secure undercover car space
AMENITIES
Residents of the Watergate North complex have access to a swimming pool, sauna, spa, gymnasium, and outdoor entertaining area.
LOCATION
The Victoria Harbour precinct is a great mix of retail and office spaces making it ideal for those who work in the area or the nearby CBD. You have an array of excellent Bourke Street restaurants and cafes right at your doorstep, while youre also close to Woolworths Victoria Harbour, harbourside restaurants, Marvel Stadium, The Hub @ Docklands, Docklands Sports Courts, Harbour Esplanade trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293 or Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to discuss this property further

82m²

Description:
Two levels of standout modern living with huge terrace!
Enjoying a position right next to The District Docklands and offering two levels of stunning Docklands living with a sleek and modern edge, this semi renovated 2 bedroom apartment is a NewQuay precinct prize with incredible alfresco highlights!
Love the expansive entertainers terrace which has space of 45sqm (approx) that is so rare to find in Docklands living
Light fills the open plan living zone where you can have separate spaces for lounge and meals
Tranquil gas fireplace services the lounge room
Designer kitchen has a sleek black motif complemented by white stone benchtops and stainless steel appliances
2nd north-facing balcony off the meals area provides even more outdoor flexibility
Both bedrooms with BIRs have an upstairs location and are separated by the stylish bathroom
Additional upstairs powder room
European laundry
Reverse cycle heating/cooling
Stylish flooring and quality carpet
Secure intercom entry
2 secure car spaces
2 storage cages
LOCATION
Youre an easy stroll to The District Docklands which features Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct with The Market which has butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also close to Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading universities, trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and Skybus to Melbourne Airport.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 or Serena Su on 0499 083 362 to discuss this property further

131.5m²
